    "description": "Menzies Aviation India Asia Pacific Associates is actively seeking a talented and motivated Hotel Manager to join our dynamic team in Pimpri-Chinchwad. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Menzies Aviation India Asia Pacific Associates:\nMenzies Aviation India Asia Pacific Associates is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in PMS Systems\n• Proficiency in Yield Management\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Learning & development budget\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pimpri-Chinchwad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Menzies Aviation India Asia Pacific Associates!",
